§ A/B-TEST-PLAN

  § CANARY
    canary-pct       : 10%
    selection        : session-id-hash mod 10 == 0  (deterministic per-session)
    duration         : ≥ 1k classify-calls per-SP per-session
    SP-set           : {SP-1 intent, SP-2 cocreative, SP-3 spontaneous}
                       ≡ SP-4 dm-arbiter + SP-5 gm-pacing stay-stage-0 W7

  § METRICS
    M-1 disagreement : |out_stage1 - out_stage0| / |out_stage0|  per-SP-avg
    M-2 perf-delta   : p95(stage-1) / p95(stage-0) - 1.0
    M-3 satisfaction : explicit-feedback ⊕ implicit-completion-rate

  § GRADUATE-CRITERIA  ⟪ ∀ W! satisfied per-SP ⟫
    ✓ M-1 < 2%       behavior-non-drift
    ✓ M-2 < 50%      latency-overhead bounded
    ✓ M-3 > 0        player-experience non-regressed
    on-graduate      : canary-pct → 100% per-SP ; stage-0 STAYS resident

  § ROLLBACK-TRIGGERS (11_KAN_RIDE § ROLL-BACK § TRIGGERS)
    T-1 latency        : p95(stage-1) > 100ms over 30-sample-window
    T-2 disagreement   : divergence > 5% over canary-window
    T-3 sovereign-byp  : sovereign.bypass-event ≥ 1 mid-canary
    T-4 invariant-fail : I-1..I-6 violated → immediate-revert
    T-5 player-revoke  : Settings → Intelligence → "Use stage-0" toggle

